datasets.name: 2da2fc8a
queryLines:
SELECT 
    *, 
    DATE_DIFF(YEAR, `生年月日to`, `健診年月日to`) AS `年齢`
FROM
  `ndb_poc`.`tokuteikenshin`.`health_checkup`
WHERE
  `生年月日to` IS NOT NULL
  AND `健診年月日to` IS NOT NULL

datasets.name: 0f15a35c
queryLines:
SELECT
  `都道府県コード`,
  AVG(DATE_DIFF(YEAR, `生年月日to`, `健診年月日to`)) AS `平均年齢`,
  AVG(`身長9n001`) AS `平均身長`,
  AVG(`体重9n006`) AS `平均体重`,
  AVG(`bmi9n011`) AS `平均BMI`,
  AVG(`収縮期血圧(1回目)9a7501回目`) AS `平均収縮期血圧`,
  AVG(`拡張期血圧(1回目)9a7601回目`) AS `平均拡張期血圧`
FROM
  `ndb_poc`.`tokuteikenshin`.`health_checkup`
WHERE
  `生年月日to` IS NOT NULL
  AND `健診年月日to` IS NOT NULL
  AND `身長9n001` IS NOT NULL
  AND `体重9n006` IS NOT NULL
  AND `bmi9n011` IS NOT NULL
  AND `収縮期血圧(1回目)9a7501回目` IS NOT NULL
  AND `拡張期血圧(1回目)9a7601回目` IS NOT NULL
  AND `都道府県コード` IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
  `都道府県コード`

datasets.name: d08f09dd
queryLines:
SELECT
  `都道府県コード`,
  `男女区分to`,
  AVG(try_divide(DATEDIFF(`健診年月日to`, `生年月日to`), 365.25)) AS `平均年齢`
FROM
  `ndb_poc`.`tokuteikenshin`.`health_checkup`
WHERE
  `健診年月日to` IS NOT NULL
  AND `生年月日to` IS NOT NULL
  AND `都道府県コード` IS NOT NULL
  AND `男女区分to` IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
  `都道府県コード`,
  `男女区分to`
ORDER BY
  `都道府県コード`;
